":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學英文真係要提起興趣先  咁先有動力 <br />\n再令到自己變左習慣<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係好快會放棄</blockquote><br />\n我相信短期內都會有動力，但係都好睇我生唔生性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9effd7e493b4a495eb79e5d9027cee8a569176e5","tid":188063,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 比d掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117a58f4693c9984aca730b0ed9f73f30d2778d3","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比多個建議你 搵啲自己有興趣睇既書 睇唔明就一路查字典一路睇 做自己鐘意/有興趣既野 會幫助好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實最有用又最快捷既方法係同啲鬼講多啲野 唔好成日諗住驚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以後我見到有外國客都會盡力試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,多謝你巴打"},{"pid":"b231d036db89d30a9212921bb698287e06abe30e","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先背7000個常見生字打底 然後趁仲記得就去睇英文書 或者 雜誌 或者睇鬼佬片唔開字幕 之後就大功告成</blockquote><br />\n每日100個 隔日溫返書啊</blockquote><br />\n我見好多人都推薦呢個方法，咁我仲想問下要唔要背下啲字首字根？ 多謝巴打你嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fce8928fe00ee60a8af2a1f00c0782d3f6763ba","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小學程度英文已經勁過大部分大學生</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦<br />\n講埋呢啲無根無據嘅嘢，仲要話大部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你真係當大學生冇讀過中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗絕絕絕大部份大學生都一定好過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38f39b12229f12c5e9c2ab9031f5e54e2d927b","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油 比d掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49e8f34d5daf3503785c0d004b83ef662d1e753","tid":188063,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"簡單，想學好一定係基本學起<br />\n小一幫到你<br />\n但讀到中學水平都要5年時間以上"},{"pid":"3262efdb0c0a5210116dc7dde4204cfe547238c7","tid":188063,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"最重要係恆心，不斷查字典<br />\n每日用不少於六小時，包括背字<br />\n你個lv學好文法先<br />\n做藍色個本English Grammar in Use<br />\n<br />\n有咩可問<br />\n利申：用兩年時間由英文垃到入讀港大法律"},{"pid":"d9c7bc25d0b80fd4e9899b495fafd1abe3c37a3c","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單，想學好一定係基本學起<br />\n小一幫到你<br />\n但讀到中學水平都要5年時間以上</blockquote><br />\n時間應該都唔係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴士"},{"pid":"a1bef1fd8b8da35c6c3c7c43ef8cc6a2321cc9f3","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最重要係恆心，不斷查字典<br />\n每日用不少於六小時，包括背字<br />\n你個lv學好文法先<br />\n做藍色個本English Grammar in Use<br />\n<br />\n有咩可問<br />\n利申：用兩年時間由英文垃到入讀港大法律</blockquote><br />\n我係現實最欣賞巴打你呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日放工去書店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd72fecc55f5554b6a0a16d056a2bfe695e9fb30","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簡單，想學好一定係基本學起<br />\n小一幫到你<br />\n但讀到中學水平都要5年時間以上</blockquote><br />\n時間應該都唔係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴<span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef962d8a2b94d323af9245064ff1bb010c2711ca","tid":188063,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小學程度英文已經勁過大部分大學生</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦<br />\n講埋呢啲無根無據嘅嘢，仲要話大部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你真係當大學生冇讀過中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多人就係讀過中學英文先變差"},{"pid":"f4cc7382e6a1ee9f451c5733c5eac243b381708a","tid":188063,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上Reddit/4chan</blockquote><br />\n呢個啱</blockquote><br />\n係唔係類似外國嘅連登？好似幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打們</blockquote><br />\n好多grammar錯自己睇路"},{"pid":"8588a61dec7dbc4491acc09b69051eaff764a4be","tid":188063,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最重要係恆心，不斷查字典<br />\n每日用不少於六小時，包括背字<br />\n你個lv學好文法先<br />\n做藍色個本English Grammar in Use<br />\n<br />\n有咩可問<br />\n利申：用兩年時間由英文垃到入讀港大法律</blockquote><br />\n我係現實最欣賞巴打你呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日放工去書店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見巴打咁客氣，講多兩句<br />\n如果英文有咁上下（中學程度左右）可以試睇SCMP<br />\n特別睇左editorial個版先<br />\n記住要不斷查字典同記字<br />\n每日用六小時左右<br />\n但每日全日溫英文效率會愈來愈慢，連睇連查字連背字六小時差不多<br />\n覺得scmp已經難你唔到記轉睇the economists，一樣係瘋狂查字<br />\n去咁識返咁上下嘅字就去睇新聞練聽力（pearl/BBC, you name it)一開頭唔好睇字幕就咁聽，聽唔到重聽，聽唔到再重聽，去到幾十次都聽唔到就睇字幕，最後要重新聽多次了解點解自己聽唔到<br />\n記住呢個過程好撚痛苦，但捱過左你英文一定好過唔少裡學生<br />\n<br />\n最後其實有個advanced step ，不過上面講嘅野你做到已經好夠<br />\n另外查字有時未必幫你明到篇文講乜，句構嘅小心分SVO（subject verb object)，每句只有一個，其他多為adjective/ adverb clause、noun clause or adverb participle phrase，咁會有助理解每句講咩，每段講咩就睇topic sentence，每篇文講咩就要靠語感去感受，會發現同睇中文一樣，有啲諷刺反話文章要留意，以及醉翁之意不在酒"},{"pid":"4006a421bd1f2b38909d7d435a3b5e4a18f42633","tid":188063,"uid":74484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最重要係恆心，不斷查字典<br />\n每日用不少於六小時，包括背字<br />\n你個lv學好文法先<br />\n做藍色個本English Grammar in Use<br />\n<br />\n有咩可問<br />\n利申：用兩年時間由英文垃到入讀港大法律</blockquote><br />\n我係現實最欣賞巴打你呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日放工去書店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見巴打咁客氣，講多兩句<br />\n如果英文有咁上下（中學程度左右）可以試睇SCMP<br />\n特別睇左editorial個版先<br />\n記住要不斷查字典同記字<br />\n每日用六小時左右<br />\n但每日全日溫英文效率會愈來愈慢，連睇連查字連背字六小時差不多<br />\n覺得scmp已經難你唔到記轉睇the economists，一樣係瘋狂查字<br />\n去咁識返咁上下嘅字就去睇新聞練聽力（pearl/BBC, you name it)一開頭唔好睇字幕就咁聽，聽唔到重聽，聽唔到再重聽，去到幾十次都聽唔到就睇字幕，最後要重新聽多次了解點解自己聽唔到<br />\n記住呢個過程好撚痛苦，但捱過左你英文一定好過唔少裡學生<br />\n<br />\n最後其實有個advanced step ，不過上面講嘅野你做到已經好夠<br />\n另外查字有時未必幫你明到篇文講乜，句構嘅小心分SVO（subject verb object)，每句只有一個，其他多為adjective/ adverb clause、noun clause or adverb participle phrase，咁會有助理解每句講咩，每段講咩就睇topic sentence，每篇文講咩就要靠語感去感受，會發現同睇中文一樣，有啲諷刺反話文章要留意，以及醉翁之意不在酒</blockquote><br />\n巴打打咁大篇文教我要點做真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 容許我copy低以後每點做<br />\n唔知點解你有啲似蕭叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我錯覺"},{"pid":"30a5d541e6bdb05d4b43aef2268db5b5971d427b","tid":188063,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"有關聽力訓練<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FGo_lm4l_yA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFGo_lm4l_yA&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8e3f929d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FGo_lm4l_yA</a><br />\n<br />\n有關句構：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AkHtljamHLE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAkHtljamHLE&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=42dac87f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AkHtljamHLE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LT9ecFSFfPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLT9ecFSFfPY&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3ac665f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LT9ecFSFfPY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pnVZWdKNMDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpnVZWdKNMDM&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6196b41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pnVZWdKNMDM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lia9hYYdhBU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLia9hYYdhBU&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=040ab69d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lia9hYYdhBU</a><br />\n<br />\n蕭愷一都有其他啲grammar影片應該岩巴打，不過最值得睇係呢幾個，只要有恆心，兩年內必有收穫，我就係成功例子，巴打加油"},{"pid":"78fa7dbdff7c230085a60e765f44e286a94817e9","tid":188063,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最重要係恆心，不斷查字典<br />\n每日用不少於六小時，包括背字<br />\n你個lv學好文法先<br />\n做藍色個本English Grammar in Use<br />\n<br />\n有咩可問<br />\n利申：用兩年時間由英文垃到入讀港大法律</blockquote><br />\n我係現實最欣賞巴打你呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日放工去書店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見巴打咁客氣，講多兩句<br />\n如果英文有咁上下（中學程度左右）可以試睇SCMP<br />\n特別睇左editorial個版先<br />\n記住要不斷查字典同記字<br />\n每日用六小時左右<br />\n但